The example views are not built by default.  Note that some view-related Ambari 2.4.0 artifacts need to be installed prior to building the examples (I guess @jaysensharma already has this).

```
# pre-req
pushd ~/tmp
curl -O http://archive.apache.org/dist/ambari/ambari-2.4.0/apache-ambari-2.4.0-src.tar.gz
tar xzf apache-ambari-2.4.0-src.tar.gz
pushd apache-ambari-2.4.0-src
mvn -am -pl ambari-views -DskipTests install
popd
popd

# now the example views
cd ambari-views/examples
mvn clean package
...
```
